  "text": "Relations between high-order moments of velocity fluctuations and structure functions Previously, § 2.4 summarised the results from [CITATION_1] for the general behaviour of higher-order velocity fluctuations. Following their work, it is fruitful to develop the limit of structure functions at r δ, by making use of the binomial theorem:",
